notesStmt.note: In this workshop discussion representatives of European youth organizations as well as experts from European institutions discuss youth issues in Europe, particularly the job situation of young people. The event is part of a symposium on youth and employment. S1 is the chair and guides the discussion, S2 takes notes. As this is the second smaller discussion round, the participants know each other from the earlier sessions and a friendly atmosphere prevails.

equipment.p: Portable minidisc recorder with electret condenser stereo microphone
